en_194343_0	Four persons including a woman were injured in a hand grenade attack which was carried out targeting a house in Bohingamuwa, Kuliyapitiya.
en_194343_1	The attack was carried out at around 9.45 pm yesterday (Jul 01) and the injured were admitted to Kuliyapitiya Hospital.
en_194343_2	The attacker has been identified.
en_194343_3	Police said that the suspect had attended a wedding ceremony last night and he had involved in a clash with another group there.
en_194343_4	Thereafter, he had thrown a hand grenade at a house.
en_194343_5	The suspect has fled the area following the incident.
